"This section documents the flag coverage of Asterinas's implementation of "
"Linux system calls. It introduces [**System Call Matching Language (SCML)**]"
"(system-call-matching-language.md), a lightweight domain‑specific language "
"for specifying allowed and disallowed patterns of system‑call invocations."
